1. Introduction

The QUENNE STACKED INTELLIGENCE framework provides a layered cognitive architecture that aligns physics, software, algorithms, and ethics. This document presents a detailed technical architecture and implementation plan for a hybrid unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) capable of long-endurance surveillance and high-speed missile interception. The design leverages each layer of the QUENNE stack to achieve unparalleled performance, adaptability, and ethical compliance.

2. System Architecture Overview

